03:08.146 --> 03:09.773
Oh, yeah. Remember?

03:09.856 --> 03:11.858
You cried in
the Abraham Lincoln thing.

03:11.942 --> 03:15.992
Hey, he was a great president,
and it was the first robot I ever saw.

