surprise, surprise-

03:24.955 --> 03:27.583
and I ended up
taking them on my own.

03:27.666 --> 03:30.465
Claire's biggest fear
was running into the evil queen.

03:30.544 --> 03:33.764
My biggest fear
was that I married her.

03:33.839 --> 03:38.265
Okay, people over 46 inches,
first stop- Indiana Jones!

03:38.385 --> 03:41.138
- Have fun on the teacups, Lily.
- Okay, let's do this.

03:41.221 --> 03:43.815
Oh, okay, wait.
Just a second here, everybody.

03:44.433 --> 03:46.151
All right.

03:47.310 --> 03:49.563
Is that a leash?
No, it's a child safety tether.

03:49.646 --> 03:51.148
This way, sweetie.

03:51.231 --> 03:53.950
