still look amazing.

05:15.732 --> 05:17.860
Does he? I hadn't noticed.

05:17.943 --> 05:20.742
Did you know
that Ethan plays the trumpet?

05:20.821 --> 05:23.745
No great surprise
with those lips of his, huh?

05:23.824 --> 05:26.623
Coo-coo-ca-choo,
Mrs. Robinson.

05:26.701 --> 05:28.703
