with a hot wife?

06:18.295 --> 06:21.845
Well, well, well. What do you know? Another
caring parent with a child safety tether.

06:21.923 --> 06:23.550
See? We're not
the only people who use them.

06:23.675 --> 06:26.394
Hi! Aren't they adorable?
Oh, and look at your cutie!

06:26.469 --> 06:28.312
Oh, well, yes.
She just wanted to say hi.

06:28.388 --> 06:30.106
Oh. Sorry.
They're a little feisty today.

06:30.181 --> 06:33.060
- Oh! No problem. She's friendly.
- Oh. Rex, gentle.

06:33.143 --> 06:35.566
