- Yeah.

06:35.645 --> 06:37.522
Okay. Lily. No, sweetie-
Lily, um-

06:37.647 --> 06:39.820
Sorry. He just gets excited.
Oh, yeah, no- Oh, no problem.

06:39.900 --> 06:41.823
Lily, stop moving, sweetie.
Stop moving.

06:41.943 --> 06:44.867
