was a lot of sharp turns and big drops.

08:06.277 --> 08:07.745
Uh-huh. Uh-huh.
It just kept going.

08:07.862 --> 08:10.991
Wow. You okay? Great.
Why wouldn't I be?

08:11.116 --> 08:14.620
Because you're kind of leaning on me.
isn't that what a marriage is?

08:14.703 --> 08:16.956
Oh, Alex,
stop touching him.

08:17.831 --> 08:19.333
You look like hell.

08:19.416 --> 08:20.963
Feel a little dizzy.

08:21.042 --> 08:22.510
I think that ride
did something to me.

08:22.585 --> 08:24.178
Fluid in your inner ear
is thickening.

08:24.295 --> 08:26.138
That's what happens when you get old.
It is?

08:26.214 --> 08:28.182
Yeah,
you can't take the motion.

08:28.258 --> 08:30.681
I gotta pop a Dramamine
to get in my swivel chair.

08:30.760 --> 08:33.808
That is not it.
I'm king of the roller coasters.

08:33.929 --> 08:37.230
I think I just put too big of a whipped
cream smile on my pancake this morning.

08:37.350 --> 08:40.854
You guys wanna go on Matterhorn? Luke, I think
me and your dad are gonna sit this one out,

08:40.937 --> 08:42.438
maybe get one of them
big pickles.

08:42.522 --> 08:45.492
No! You're gonna have to eat
that pickle on your own, Jay.

08:45.567 --> 08:47.490
I still got
a few good years left.

08:47.569 --> 08:50.448
Luke, wait up!
I'll race you there!

08:53.116 --> 08:54.618
I'm good. I'm good.

08:58.872 --> 09:00.670
Okay, everybody's looking at us.

09:00.790 --> 09:04.090
I haven't been judged by this many people
since I forgot my canvas bags at Whole Foods.

09:04.169 --> 09:06.388
Yeah. Well, maybe they're staring
because we have what they want.

09:06.463 --> 09:08.636
Wh- Oh, a pet daughter.
Is that-

09:08.715 --> 09:10.217
You know, I don't care
what people think.

09:10.300 --> 09:11.768
