I think it's a mistake.

09:22.854 --> 09:25.528
But I don't want you to run away,
'cause that would be very, very unsafe.

09:25.607 --> 09:30.078
And if we lost you, you'd be very scared,
and we'd be very sad, okay?

09:30.195 --> 09:31.663
Okay.
All right.

09:31.738 --> 09:35.163
See, Cam? You treat her
like a human being, and she acts like one.

09:35.241 --> 09:36.538
Chip 'n' Dale!

09:36.618 --> 09:39.337
Oh, great.
Now she's chasing squirrels. Lily!

09:39.454 --> 09:41.877
Honey, come on!
Lily! Lily!

09:47.087 --> 09:50.591
- Hey, how was Splash Mountain?
- It was great. Maybe we go again.

09:50.673 --> 09:52.675
No, thanks.
There was no reception in there.

09:52.759 --> 09:54.853
You know how many bars I had?
Zip-a-dee-doo-dah.

09:54.928 --> 09:56.930
Reuben, talk to me!

09:57.013 --> 09:59.937
Must be nice to
get out of those shoes for a minute.

10:00.016 --> 10:01.814
I don't know what
you're talking about.

10:01.893 --> 10:03.486
Nothing. I'm just
making conversation.

10:03.561 --> 10:05.563
Hey. Check it out.

10:05.647 --> 10:10.403
I bought one of those souvenir photos
with you and Manny on the ride.

10:10.485 --> 10:12.533
Boy, it looks like
you're having a good time.

10:12.612 --> 10:14.614
Wait a minute.
What's that in your hand?

10:14.697 --> 10:16.199
Are those shoes?

10:16.282 --> 10:18.034
I'm not even sure
that that is us, Jay.

10:18.118 --> 10:19.665
