on the other side of the park.

10:34.884 --> 10:36.386
I'm fine.

10:36.469 --> 10:38.892
You just try
to keep up with us.

10:39.848 --> 10:42.522
I can't take this.

10:44.811 --> 10:46.905
Dad, throw your hands up! it's fun!

10:46.980 --> 10:48.948
Oh, yeah, it is fun!

10:49.065 --> 10:51.033
Hey! Yeah!

10:51.109 --> 10:52.110
Whoo!
Hey.

10:52.193 --> 10:56.448
Whoa! Whoo!
Whoo-hoo-hoo!

10:56.531 --> 11:01.162
