your jacket when I'm cold.

11:43.119 --> 11:45.668
Such a good man, Jay.
Thank you.

11:45.747 --> 11:46.873
Mmm.

11:48.249 --> 11:50.001
Wow.

11:50.084 --> 11:52.883
