Oh.
What was that?

21:02.762 --> 21:03.854
Whoo!

21:05.347 --> 21:08.567
This is gonna be so awesome!
Whoo! Hey!

21:11.937 --> 21:14.565
Close your eyes.
It makes it more fun.

21:14.648 --> 21:16.275
